page1.title: About Me
page1.content: I’m a 32 year old Data Scientist living in Copenhagen, Denmark. . I spend the my workdays in a week doing Data Science at Nuuday, and usually some of my weekend tinkering with Data Science related stuff as well — epsecially now that the Covid-19 pandemic imposes the social distancing measures. . Hope you’ll follow along on my blog, and fee free to reach out to me if you’d like to get in contact! . Me, other places on the internet . Github | Quora | LinkedIn | StackOverFlow | .
